S.FORM: Bob Brannum nalecuhan i Winfield, Kansas, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput. 5 bulad 28 demiad, 1925 a mihca, Bob Brannum, miunduay. (mapatay i 2005 a mihca) namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
